OL,3,CBritain's forced adoption scandal: Why
OL,4,Cwon't the government say sorry?
OL,6,FOther countries where forced adoption
OL,7,Ftook place have already issued a
OL,8,Fformal apology but Westminster has
OL,9,Fdone nothing, ITV News Social Affairs
OL,10,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker reports
OL,12,FOver the past 12 months, ITV News has
OL,13,Fheard heartbreaking testimony from
OL,14,Funmarried mothers whose children were
OL,15,Ftaken, and adult adoptees who are
OL,16,Fstill searching for the truth.
OL,18,FTheir calls for an official government
OL,19,Fapology for the state's role in this
OL,20,Fcruel practice which lasted for four
OL,21,Fdecades continue to go unanswered.
