OL,6,F"And the day she died, I found out
OL,7,Fthat my entire life was a lie and they
OL,8,Fweren't my parents, they weren't my
OL,9,Ffamily. And that I came from somewhere
OL,10,Felse."
OL,12,FIn 1961, her mother was one of
OL,13,Fhundreds of thousands of women forced
OL,14,Fto put their babies up for adoption.
OL,15,FJacqui was just a few weeks old when
OL,16,Fshe was adopted.
