OL,3,CBritain's forced adoption scandal: Why
OL,4,Cwon't the government say sorry?
OL,6,FThe group Movement for an Adoption
OL,7,FApology (MAA) also want specialist
OL,8,Fsupport for those affected including
OL,9,Ftrauma informed counselling services,
OL,10,Fhelp with reunions and tracing as well
OL,11,Fas easier access to historical records.
OL,13,FJacqui Adams said an apology from the
OL,14,Fgovernment is 'just the beginning' and
OL,15,Fwould need to be in a public arena
OL,17,FIn 2021, the Irish Taoiseach Micheal
OL,18,FMartin apologised for the "profound
OL,19,Fgenerational wrong visited upon Irish
OL,20,Fmothers and their children".
