OL,10,FFoley told ITV News of the importance
OL,11,Fof recognising the state's role this
OL,12,Fscandal.
OL,14,F"We are mindful we will never be able
OL,15,Fto do enough, but we have to do
OL,16,Fsomething that acknowledges what
OL,17,Fhappened and that we are cognicent of
OL,18,Fall that had to be endured," she said.
