OL,3,CBritain's forced adoption scandal: Why
OL,4,Cwon't the government say sorry?
OL,6,F"I don't understand why they are
OL,7,Freluctant, because a verbal apology is
OL,8,Fprobably the easiest thing to do and I
OL,9,Fsay this with no disrespect, apologies
OL,10,Fare hollow unless they are followed up
OL,11,Fwith action," said Ms Carey.
OL,13,F"I think many governments look at
OL,14,Fapologies in regards to what it might
OL,15,Fcost the state. And that becomes the
OL,16,Fmeasurement of how are we going to
OL,17,Fresponse to these people."
OL,19,FMs Carey told ITV News that she
OL,20,Fbelieved it "ultimately it comes to
OL,21,Fdown money".
