OL,6,FThe MAA recently instructed human
OL,7,Frights and public interest litigation
OL,8,Ffirm McCue Jury & Partners to explore
OL,9,Flegal options.
OL,11,FDr Michael Lambert from Lancaster
OL,12,FUniversity has spent a decade
OL,13,Fexamining these institutions including
OL,14,Fhow they were funded and operated.
OL,16,FHe described how unmarried mothers
OL,17,Fwere treated as "second class" and
OL,18,Fweren't entitled to the same level of
OL,19,Fhealth treatment, social security or
OL,20,Fhousing as married women.
